This error happens because of this line:

    uri = uri.replace(queryParameters: params);

The purpose of that is to replace the uri parameters for new ones, here is an example:

    var uri = Uri.parse(&quot;http://www.example.com/?q=test&quot;);
    final replaceParams = {&quot;q&quot;:&quot;othertest&quot;};
    uri = uri.replace(queryParameters: replaceParams);
    print(uri);

The output would be:

    I/flutter ( 6060): http://www.example.com/?q=othertest

So, these are parameters for `GET` requests. 


----------


In your case you are confusing the `uri.replace()` for `GET` parameters and passing the `POST` parameters there. So, it seems that you don&#39;t need to call the `uri.replace()` method and that would solve this error.

